1121
00:56:56.390 --> 00:56:57.250
Duke./
Tidak.

1122
00:56:57.286 --> 00:56:58.723
Duke?/
Tidak mau!

1123
00:56:58.823 --> 00:57:00.456
Duke!/
Tidak.

